<div class="section">
<h2>Recommended Guide</h2>
<P>If you have the Player's Guide that's the first choice, but the way it's formatted I wouldn't recommend it if you don't have a physical copy. Plus it has <a href="https://starmen.net/mother2/gameinfo/guideerrors/">a number of typos</a> and says the Kraken can drop the Gutsy Bat, when in reality only the Bionic Kraken (later in the game) can. Overall, I'd recommend the <a href="http://walkthrough.starmen.net/earthbound/">Starmen.net EarthBound walkthrough</a> as it is print-friendly and addresses some of the things you might need to watch out for (like getting the Sword of Kings).</p>
